Class GwtResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.esoco.ewt.app.GwtResource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Resource

    public class GwtResource
extends java.lang.Object
implements Resource
    A GWT-specific resource class that performs string lookups in a resource of type ConstantsWithLookup and image lookups in a map with ImageResource entries.
